import pandas as pd
from datetime import timedelta

def format(path):
    # Read the CSV file
    df = pd.read_csv(path)
    
    # Convert the 4th column to datetime and subtract 3 hours
    df.iloc[:, 3] = pd.to_datetime(df.iloc[:, 3]) - timedelta(hours=3)
    
    # Write the adjusted data to an Excel file
    df.to_excel('/workspace/audit-export.xlsx', index=False)
